Not true, it's not only on ReiserFS and disk failures.
I also saw this behaviour on proc:
$ cat /proc/dri/0/vma
for example.
000  1000 15186 14534   9   0  1272  368 down   D    pts/0      0:00 cat 0/vma
In such cases, just forget that tty.
